- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another likely category as the paper deals with learning effective policies for complex tasks. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is a possible category as the paper may involve visual perception for the manipulation tasks. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also a possible category as the paper deals with controlling robotic systems.
